The new Star Fox Zero is almost here! And with help from my friend JC of the Nintendo Treehouse, I'm gaining some early access to show you all my awesome moves. Also, JC answers YOUR questions and shows us some cool hidden features.

Special Thanks to JC and the Nintendo Treehouse team for joining us for making this episode possible.
